| **Phase** | **Task**                              | **Description / Deliverables**                                                                                                                                                                                 | **Estimated Duration** |
| --------- | ------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------- |
| 1         | Requirement Analysis                  | Understand business requirements, collect sample slips, identify supported document formats (e-PDF, scanned PDF, images), finalize 10–15 fields to be extracted, identify edge cases and expected output JSON. | **2 Days**             |
| 2         | Solution Design & Architecture        | Finalize overall system architecture, processing flow, API flow, database design, OCR strategy, OpenAI integration approach, and vector storage design.                                                        | **1 Day**              |
| 3         | PostgreSQL Database Design            | Create PostgreSQL database, design tables for uploaded documents, extraction jobs, extracted fields, embeddings, audit logs, indexes, and relationships.                                                       | **2 Days**             |
| 4         | FastAPI Project Setup                 | Create backend project structure, configure environment variables, database connectivity, logging, Swagger documentation, and reusable project modules.                                                        | **2 Days**             |
| 5         | File Upload Module                    | Develop upload API, validate file types, save documents, generate job IDs, update document metadata, and return upload status to frontend.                                                                     | **2 Days**             |
| 6         | Document Classification               | Identify uploaded document type (text PDF vs scanned PDF), route documents to OCR or PDF parser accordingly, and maintain processing status.                                                                   | **1 Day**              |
| 7         | OCR Integration                       | Integrate Azure Document Intelligence, process scanned documents, extract text/tables/layout, store raw OCR output, and handle OCR exceptions.                                                                 | **3 Days**             |
| 8         | PDF Parsing                           | Implement parser for searchable PDFs, extract page-wise text, clean unnecessary content, and combine with OCR pipeline where applicable.                                                                       | **2 Days**             |
| 9         | Text Cleaning & Preprocessing         | Normalize extracted text, remove noise, preserve page mapping, clean formatting, and prepare standardized text for downstream processing.                                                                      | **2 Days**             |
| 10        | Chunking Strategy                     | Implement document chunking with configurable size and overlap, preserve metadata (page number, chunk ID), and prepare chunks for embeddings.                                                                  | **2 Days**             |
| 11        | Embedding Generation & Vector Storage | Integrate embedding model, generate embeddings, configure pgvector in PostgreSQL, store vectors, and create vector indexes for retrieval.                                                                      | **3 Days**             |
| 12        | OpenAI Integration                    | Integrate Azure OpenAI/OpenAI APIs, implement prompt templates, retry mechanisms, JSON validation, response parsing, and reusable AI service layer.                                                            | **2 Days**             |
| 13        | Field Extraction Engine               | Develop extraction logic for required business fields, generate structured JSON output, validate extracted values, capture confidence scores, and map source references.                                       | **4 Days**             |
| 14        | Result Storage                        | Store extracted fields, confidence scores, page references, processing status, and maintain complete extraction history in PostgreSQL.                                                                         | **1 Day**              |
| 15        | API Development                       | Build APIs for extraction trigger, processing status, document details, extraction results, and reprocessing support for frontend integration.                                                                 | **3 Days**             |
| 16        | Error Handling & Logging              | Implement centralized exception handling, audit logging, retry logic, timeout handling, and detailed processing logs for troubleshooting.                                                                      | **2 Days**             |
| 17        | Testing & Validation                  | Test with multiple document types (searchable PDFs, scanned PDFs, poor-quality scans, multi-page documents), validate extraction accuracy, and optimize prompts/chunking.                                      | **4 Days**             |
| 18        | Documentation & Knowledge Transfer    | Prepare API documentation, database schema documentation, deployment guide, setup instructions, and technical handover documents.                                                                              | **2 Days**             |
| 19        | End-to-End Integration & Demo         | Perform complete system testing, frontend-backend integration validation, bug fixing, performance optimization, and prepare final project demonstration.                                                       | **3 Days**             |
